caption:
Houston’s Bush Intercontinental Airport has officially renamed Terminal A in honor of the late Congresswoman Sheila Jackson Lee, recognizing her decades of tireless service, fearless advocacy, and unwavering dedication to justice.⁠
⁠
From Capitol Hill to the city of Houston, her legacy continues to uplift the community she served. 🕊️⁠
⁠
Tap the 🔗 in bio to learn more about the woman behind this historic honor.⁠
